OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FDFDS did not consult the Governments
OL,8,Fof Guernsey or Jersey over plans to
OL,9,Fintroduce a weekend inter-island
OL,10,Fservice, according to a senior
OL,11,Fpolitician.
OL,13,FDeputy Sasha Kazantseva-Miller, the
OL,14,FPresident of Guernsey's Economic
OL,15,FDevelopment Committee, says they had
OL,16,Fno choice but to reject the company's
OL,17,Fplans as they were "undeliverable".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FIn a statement on Wednesday, the
OL,8,FCommittee said DFDS wanted to run a
OL,9,Fservice from Jersey to Guernsey on a
OL,10,FFriday night, with a return trip to
OL,11,FJersey in the late afternoon on Monday.
OL,13,FHowever, as Deputy Kazantseva-Miller
OL,14,Fexplains, this would have involved
OL,15,Fport workers staying beyond their
OL,16,Fregular shifts - creating extra costs
OL,17,Fand staffing pressures.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FShe says: "The majority of those
OL,8,Farrivals or departures would be
OL,9,Foutside the official operating hours
OL,10,Fof Ports of Guernsey and the
OL,11,FImmigration and Customs departments,
OL,12,Fso they immediately presented some
OL,13,Fchallenging operational requirements
OL,14,Ffor our ports, which made it basically
OL,15,Fundeliverable.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,F"What's important is that these
OL,8,Fproposals have not been developed with
OL,9,Fany form of consultation with either
OL,10,Fthe Government of Jersey or the
OL,11,FGovernment of Guernsey or Guernsey
OL,12,FPorts, so they came out of the blue.
OL,14,F"We're actually quite disappointed
OL,15,Fthat despite the rhetoric about
OL,16,Fcollaboration and working together, we
OL,17,Fhaven't been engaged in the
OL,18,Fdevelopment of this proposal at all.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,F"We would have clearly outlined that
OL,8,Foperational considerations have to be
OL,9,Ftaken into account when proposals are
OL,10,Fdeveloped."
OL,12,FConcerns have also been raised over
OL,13,Fhow reciprocal the service would be,
OL,14,Fas Jersey residents could visit
OL,15,FGuernsey for the weekend but not the
OL,16,Fother way around.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FThe Economic Development Committee
OL,8,FPresident says Guernsey remains
OL,9,F"committed" to working with DFDS and
OL,10,Fpoliticians across the water to find a
OL,11,Fsolution, but called on the Government
OL,12,Fof Jersey to match words with action.
OL,14,FShe explains: "The rhetoric from the
OL,15,FGovernment of Jersey is about
OL,16,Fcooperation, but they have to
OL,17,Fdemonstrate that they are actually
OL,18,Factively and collaboratively working
OL,19,Fwith us on these proposals and this is
OL,20,Fjust another example of where that
OL,21,Fdidn't take place."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FPassengers, meanwhile, are
OL,8,Fdisappointed that a deal has not been
OL,9,Fstruck.
OL,11,FRyan Hidrio, from the Jersey
OL,12,FMotorcycle and Light Car Club, says
OL,13,Fnot having inter-island sailings on
OL,14,Fweekends means some events are "not
OL,15,Fviable" for competitors.
OL,17,FFor those with vehicles, there is only
OL,18,Fa Brittany Ferries inter-island
OL,19,Fsailing to and from Guernsey on a
OL,20,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1776708665
OL,3,CInter-island ferry plan
OL,4,C'undeliverable' due to times,
OL,5,Cpolitician says
OL,7,FMr Hidrio says: "Having to go for a
OL,8,Fweek at a time for just one event,
OL,9,Fit's just not viable. It's time off
OL,10,Ffrom work, it's time away from
OL,11,Ffamilies, extra costs, everything.
OL,13,F"The club relies on having a healthy
OL,14,Fentry for our events, and that works
OL,15,Fboth ways. Then the knock-on to other
OL,16,Fbusinesses, the lack of hotel nights,
OL,17,Fit goes on."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
